    "GCG-V refers to the visual version of GCG.",
    "MethodTrain ASR (%) Test ASR (%) Without Attack / 37.0 GCG [30] 68.2 50.0 VAJM [20] / 64.0 GCG-V 89.4 83.0 UMK(Ours) 100.0 96.0In Table 1, the train ASR (%) and test ASR (%) of our proposed method are compared with baseline unimodal attacks on 66 training samples from Advbench's [30] harmful behaviors and 100 test samples from the held-out set.",
